results.name: Annual Report
results.description: Comprehensive annual report including financial statements, management discussion and analysis, and other required disclosures.

results.name: Earnings Release
results.description: Periodic financial results announcement, typically quarterly or annual.

results.name: Sustainability Report
results.description: Reports on environmental, social, and governance (ESG) factors and initiatives.

results.name: Quarterly Report
results.description: Financial report for a three-month period, including financial statements and management commentary.

results.name: Half-Year Report
results.description: Financial report for a six-month period, including financial statements and management commentary.

results.name: Inside Information
results.description: Ad-hoc disclosure of material non-public information that could affect security prices.

results.name: Prospectus
results.description: Formal document required by financial regulators for public offerings of securities.

results.name: Proxy Statement
results.description: Document providing shareholders with information necessary for voting at a shareholder meeting.
